      <title>盈透证券客户可以每天 22 小时交易国债</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/interactive-brokers-clients-can-trade-treasuries-22-hours-a-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[盈透证券集团 (Interactive Brokers Group Inc.) 的客户现在可以在一周内每天 22 小时交易美国国债，因为这家电子经纪商寻求在全球范围内吸引更多客户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/interactive-brokers-clients-can-trade-treasuries-22-hours-a-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 17:30:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
